        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The people does not repudiate this shame and disgrace, but is willing to endure it patiently, since by its sin it has fully deserved it. נשׁכּבה, not: we lie, but: we will lay us down in our shame, as a man in pain and grief throws himself on the ground, or on his couch (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
